<P>
   RUSSIA-MINERS (Moscow) _ No other group embodies the frustration
with Russia's hobbling economic system as much as its coal miners,
who have held sit-ins, marched and blocked rail lines for months
over their inability to get paid _ and all to a collective national
yawn. Now it appears that their protests are beginning to bite. By
Michael Wines. (With map.)
