early-stage breast cancer avoid mastectomy, according to a new
study. By Samantha Meese. 500 words. B. MS Symptoms Worsen
Temporarily After Pregnancy : A report from Europe confirms that
childbirth has a temporary adverse effect on multiple sclerosis
symptoms. By Merritt McKinney. 500 words. 9. BREAKTHROUGH BRIEFS
