when a giant meteorite struck the Yucatan Peninsula in Mexico?
What's happening with Jupiter's Great Red Spot? A round-up of
science briefs compiled by the editors of Discover magazine. 800
words + photos. 10. ENTICING TEENS TO THE WEB Teenage girls are a
hot online market, and apparel firms are joining the party, giving
them what they like: clothes and chats with friends. By Georgia
Lee. From Women's Wear Daily. 1,500 words
