<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-03 12:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5158 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ROSENFELD-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      08-03 0863
