<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-03 13:25 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5223 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOOKS-BEEPERSPEAK-ART     08-03 1243
