   INTERNATIONAL NEWS (``w'' category)
</P>
<P>
   FRANCE-STANDSTILL (Paris) _ already filed _ Paris and other
cities are emptying out as the French head for a month at the
seashore or countryside. Those remaining in the cities are hard put
to find a doctor or dentist. Heaven help you if the toilet leaks.
The plumbers are living it up on the beaches of St. Tropez, where
no celebrity would be caught dead this time of year. By BERNARD D.
KAPLAN.
</P>
<P>
   COMMENTARY (``k'' category)
</P>
<P>
   MEANS-COLUMN (Washington) _ Both the Senate and House are so
obtuse on the subject of gun control that they ignored the recent
violent lesson right under their noses. Although lawmakers grew
emotional last week at memorial services for two police guards
slain in the Capitol, the legislators refused to connect their
hearts with their heads. By MARIANNE MEANS.
</P>
