<P>
   BBN-FEVER (Houston) _ Television ratings for Randy Johnson debut
with the Astros on Sunday were five times higher than normal.
Tickets sales are soaring for Johnson's inaugural appearance at the
Astrodome next weekend and for home games in general. After years
of indifference, the Astros are catching on in Houston. By CARA
LaBRIE.
