   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ASCEND-STRATUS (Undated) -- Stratus Computer is about to be
pulled apart, with most of its employees slated to work for a
still-to-be-named new employer under terms of an $822 million stock
acquisition by Ascend. By Ronald Rosenberg. 700 words.
</P>
